edictable someone can \nscrap our entire app\n- We can generate number randomly\n    - API sever picks a ticket server -> selects one range at random\n    - selects current of the range and then incr curreny by 1 if end!=current\nTxn\n    Select * from ranges where id = ?\n    Update ranges set current = current + 1 where id = ?\nTxn","version":603,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b3v","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"1) What if we need unique random shortCodes (which are not predictable) ?\n- INCR getting a integer -> makes generation of shortCode predictable someone can \nscrap our entire app\n- We can generate number randomly\n    - API sever picks a ticket server -> selects one range at random\n    - selects current of the range and then incr curreny by 1 if end!=current\nTxn\n    Select * from ranges where id = ?\n    Update ranges set current = current + 1 where id = ?\nTxn","height":350,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":610872534,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-5817.7422592553521,"angle":0,"y":7665.0295723360823,"width":1161.5802001953125},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","link":null,"endArrowhead":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"startBinding":null,"index":"b3w","startArrowhead":null,"backgroundColor":"transparent","endBinding":null,"angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"version":95,"roundness":{"type":2},"type":"line","updated":1782548710678,"id":"tHEr9mY1GQ0eXhvXY72XP","x":-4411.7167519029281,"seed":1505715964,"boundElements":[],"y":7732.1952519407459,"opacity":100,"height":0,"points":[[0,0],[591.7054329810735,0]],"width":591.7054329810735,"frameId":null,"polygon":false,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":798564886},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","link":null,"endArrowhead":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"startBinding":null,"ind